</td>
    <td><a name="wp3689079"> </a><div class="pCellBodyLeft" >
ASSERT_NO_OVERFLOW
</div>    
</td>
    <td><a name="wp3689081"> </a><div class="pCellBodyLeft" >
Expression changed value from <em class="cEmphasis">max</em> to a value not in the range <em class="cEmphasis">min </em>+ 1 to <em class="cEmphasis">max </em>- 1.
</div>    
</td>
</tr>
</table>
</div>
	
