<a name="wp3743831"> </a><p class="pBody" >
Ensures that <code class="cCodeBody">addr</code> does not overflow (i.e., change from a value of 4 at the rising edge of <code class="cCodeBody">clk</code> to a value of 0 or a value greater than 4 at the next rising edge of <code class="cCodeBody">clk</code>).  </p>    <div align="left"><img src="images/ovl_checkers40.gif" height="83" width="448" border="0" vspace="0" hspace="100" />  </div>	
